# mob_project

Code accompanying the paper on multi-object binding in vision-language models (CLIP). We extract CLIP embeddings from multi-object image/text datasets, train scene embeddings with controlled generalization splits, and run linear probes and complexity analyses to study how well CLIP encodes object identities and concepts compositionally.

---

